title: For the love of God, why won’t baby fever just leave me alone!
text:
by Whitney Barthel posted in Mom Stories Is it possible to have incurable baby fever? Can someone feel like they will never out-kid their desire to have more babies? And how many times can one person cry at the sight of the Huggies commercial when the doctor puts the newborn baby on the mother’s chest?... Read more »

Want to get the full story? Click on the headline above. And thanks for reading the BabyCenter Blog.
